          <title>
            <string language="en">beta-pleated sheet structure</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Beta-gefaltete Blatstruktur</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">structure bêta-plissée de feuille</string>

          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the beta-pleated sheet arrangement of polypeptide chains. This is brought about by the hydrogen bonds between amino acids.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die Beta-gefaltete 
Blattanordnung für Polypeptidketten. Dieses wird durch die 
Wasserstoffbindungen zwischen Aminosäuren hervorgebracht.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre l'agencement 
bêta-plissé de feuille des chaînes de polypeptide. Ceci est 
provoqué par les obligations d'hydrogène entre les acides aminés.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra o arranjo beta-plissado 
da folha de correntes do polypeptide. Isto é causado pelas 
ligações do hidrogênio entre aminos-ácido.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra la disposizione 
beta-pieghettata del foglio delle catene del polipeptide. Ciò 
è determinata dai legami dell'idrogeno fra gli amminoacidi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει βήτα-πτυχωμένη ρύθμιση 
φύλλων polypeptide των αλυσίδων. Αυτό επέρχεται από τους
δεσμούς υδρογόνου μεταξύ των αμινοξέων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra el arreglo beta-plisado
de la hoja de los encadenamientos del polipéptido. Esto es 
causada por los enlaces del hidrógeno entre los aminoácidos.</string>
          </description>
